data.description:
Home seekers and savvy investors, Welcome to a property that is truly a hidden gem in the real estate market. Whether you are on the lookout for your forever home or an opportunity to make a sound investment. (RE-ZONING Opportunity).  Nestled on 3.461 acres of land, it occupies a prime location at the corner of Ocotillo Rd & Meridian, offering endless possibilities and abundant potential.  As you approach this unique piece of real estate, you will be captivated by its perfect positioning and the promising opportunities it presents. The residence offers 3-bedroom, 2-bathrooms that will instantly make you feel at home.  But that's not all; prepare to be amazed by the additional features this property boasts. (CLICK MORE) A massive 1,440 square foot garage/workshop/barn awaits those who have a passion for tinkering or require ample space for storage purposes. This versatile structure has been expertly designed to cater to livestock enthusiasts and horse lovers alike - offering endless possibilities for accommodating animals comfortably while simultaneously serving as an ideal workshop space.

The expansive plot size provides ample space for various ventures - envision yourself creating your dream oasis or building additional different structures.  With such vast acreage at your disposal, there are absolutely no limitations when it comes to fulfilling your vision.
